        .col-lg-6.col-md-12
            p.mb-5.mb-lg-0 As a national distributor based near Amish country, we bring you unique home and outdoor furnishings and accents direct from Amish workshops and farms. And because we keep merchandising, inventory and marketing costs to a minimum, we’re able to pass even more savings along to you. Merchandising and inventory costs are low because we don’t operate from a brick and mortar location. When you place your order, we send it direct to our Amish friends who then create your pieces and send them directly to you. Marketing costs are low because we don’t produce fancy brochures, send repeat mailings and hire telemarketing staff to bother you. Instead, we leverage the power of the Internet to inform and educate you. Of course should you have any questions, you’re always welcome to e-mail or call.
        .col-lg-6.col-md-12
